<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>{% block title %}Measur3D - OGC API Features{% endblock %}</title>
</head>

<body>
<h1>{{ title }}</h1>
<h2> Accessing CityJSON models and their features </h2>
<p> by {{ author }} </p>
<p> A special thanks to Bart De Lathouwer for its insight and the API basics <a href="https://github.com/LudoWhereat/ogc-api-features">OGC API Features Github</a> </p>
<p>self = <a href="{{ url }}/">{{ title }}</a> (text/html)</p>
<p>alternate = <a href="{{ url }}/?f=json">{{ title }}</a> (application/json)</p>
<p>service = <a href="{{ url }}/api">the API definition (JSON)</a> (application/vnd.oai.openapi+json;version=3.0)</p>
<p>service = <a href="{{ url }}/api?f=yaml">the API definition (YAML)</a> (application/vnd.oai.openapi+json;version=3.0)</p>
<p>service = <a href="{{ url }}/api.html">the API definition (HTML)</a> (text/html)</p>
<p>conformance = <a href="{{ url }}/conformance">OGC API - Features conformance classes implemented by this server</a> (application/json)</p>
<p>data = <a href="{{ url }}/collections">Metadata about the feature collections</a> (application/json)</p>
</body>
</html>
